  "description": {
    "zh": "又见面了，士兵，我有个新任务给你。\n你知道我卖那些使用 9x39 毫米弹药的武器吧，我需要有人在夜晚测试它们。我会给你几百发优质的子弹，但别一次用完！\n\n你的任务很简单，在夜晚用这种口径的武器击杀目标，并确保你熟悉这些步枪！这不是给新手的任务。",
    "en": "Hello again warrior, I got another job for you.\nYou know that I sell these weapons that shoot 9x39mm ammunition, I need someone to try them out at night. I will give you a few hundred rounds of decent bullets, but don't use them up at once!\n\nYour task is simple, take out a bunch of targets at night while using weapons chambered in this caliber, and make sure you know how to handle these rifles! This ain't for amateurs."
  },
